# Xcode user-specific state (schemes, breakpoints, window layout) —
# this is per-developer and regenerated by Xcode on open, so tracking it
# is what causes the recurring merge conflicts.
**/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xccheckout
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.xcscmblueprint

